Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.11,0:56:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll cure everything, you know, and\Nthen when you and then you tear it down,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.24,0:56:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it kind of goes, "Oh,\Nit's uh
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.64,0:56:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I could write much better ads.\N>> I get very frustrated with the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.83,0:56:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,advertising departments of many\Ncompanies and they could get so much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.24,0:56:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,more mileage for their money. I mean\Nthey really get uh
